                  %p.margin-bottom With dynamic and responsive layouts, a thing of beauty to impress your attendees, colleagues and/or clients.
                  %label AUTOMATED WORKFLOWS
                  %p Makes it easy to measure page views, clickthrough rates, conversion rates, demographic information, and so much more.  
                .col-md-4
                  %label INFORMATION RICH
                  %p.margin-bottom Organizers can publish and update event details so your attendees make informed decisions to enhance their event experience. 
            %hr
