                  %h3 Online registration, ticketing & payments
                  %p Maximize event registrations with our simple, yet powerful event registration software.
                .col-md-4
                  %label SAVE TIME
                  %p.margin-bottom Opening, entering and sorting out illegible or inaccurate forms can be very time consuming, eliminating manual registration saves hours per event.
                  %label GET PAID FASTER
                  %p Collect payments for tickets using your account or ours. Hassle free, secure transactions to help you sell more tickets.
                .col-md-4
                  %label INCREASED ATTENDANCE
                  %p Increase the volume of attendees by up to 20% because of the ease of access to ticketing.
            %hr
